Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.69,0:00:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,☆Dragon Ball Super☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经淡忘的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今再续前缘　又开始燃亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给星星都连上线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.85,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样给宇宙画出了门框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跻身于全新的舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向诸神发出挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强烈☆猛烈☆活力满泻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Go！恐慌奔走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你输了就能变更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.88,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知天高地厚又何妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:01:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生无可悔　身无界限　一往无前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,壮烈☆激烈☆活力爆裂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Yes！拳脚不绝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去沐浴颤抖的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个壮大传说　正在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.57,0:01:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞向未来的悟空等人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.07,0:01:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遭遇了第10宇宙的界王扎马斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.29,0:01:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来你是「黑悟空」的伙伴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.54,0:01:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只不过是战友而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空和特兰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.53,0:01:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向扎马斯和「黑悟空」发起挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.86,0:01:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.72,0:01:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不死之身的肉体，就是神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.14,0:02:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赛亚人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.06,0:02:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弥次郎兵卫和小舞救出了战败的悟空等人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.45,0:02:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未来的命运将会如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.03,0:02:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而此时，现在的扎马斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告诉我关于超级龙珠的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.25,0:02:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「扎马斯和黑 越发神秘的二人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.18,0:02:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超级龙珠也叫做许愿球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.98,0:02:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于神历41年由龙神萨拉玛创造出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.71,0:02:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是直径37196.2204公里的纯球体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.03,0:03:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙和第7宇宙合计七个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在七个浅黄色的球体上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.65,0:03:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,分别有一到七个红色五角星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是界王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.16,0:03:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一旦惹怒了我，像你这种货色，我一瞬间就能干掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.68,0:03:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但…但是，有关超级龙珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.04,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你叫我把知道的一切都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.86,0:03:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我说的是使用方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使…使用方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,方…方法是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.15,0:03:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将第6、第7两个宇宙分散的七个球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.91,0:03:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全部集齐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.58,0:03:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后用神的语言念出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.01,0:03:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「出来吧神之龙，实现我们的愿望TYONMAGE」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.01,0:03:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,注：TYONMAGE=月代头，句尾加TYONMAGE是常见日式冷笑话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要说「TYONMAGE」？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要说「TYONMAGE」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.39,0:04:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神之龙就会出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.49,0:04:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以实现任何一个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.87,0:04:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后便会再次飞散于两个宇宙间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直等待着下一个有未实现梦想的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.75,0:04:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将它们集齐的时刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.28,0:04:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在超级龙珠在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,提问结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的玩笑也结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.29,0:04:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现…现在还使用不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.23,0:04:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前几日刚刚有人用过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.17,0:04:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在正处于光芒消失，没有效用的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.76,0:04:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,需要多长时间再次使用？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蟑螂从出生到死的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大…大约一年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要一年啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.27,0:04:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只能等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,耐心一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.73,0:04:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把所有许愿球的地点告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.78,0:04:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.43,0:05:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告诉我关于孙悟空那个男人的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.95,0:05:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙悟空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.88,0:05:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.89,0:05:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们回来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.89,0:05:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们去反击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白痴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们真是一群笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去战斗竟然忘记带仙豆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.03,0:05:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起啊，你们在哪里找到的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.39,0:05:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还好意思问哪里找到的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在厕所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.65,0:05:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么说来我出发前是去了一趟厕所哈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就你能干出这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.55,0:05:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我错了我错了，算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.32,0:06:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没那么容易就算了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.68,0:06:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」把你们三个都打败了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不只是「黑悟空」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有别的敌人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.31,0:06:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.73,0:06:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是扎马斯，扎马斯是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.52,0:06:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下，扎马斯就是那个和「黑悟空」气很相似
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第10宇宙的见习界王神吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.66,0:06:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还以为他是个好的界王大人，竟然是个强敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.83,0:06:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽说气很相似，不过终究是另外一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且是不死之身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不死之身？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.38,0:06:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是为什么？因为是神吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.46,0:06:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神应该不是不死之身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且「黑悟空」那个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.24,0:06:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,变身成了拥有强大力量的超级赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超级赛亚人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么样的超级赛亚人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.20,0:06:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超级赛亚人…什么来着？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桃红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对，桃红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桃红？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.07,0:07:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超级赛亚人桃红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.51,0:07:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」起的这是什么变态的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.62,0:07:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好，我们去反击吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是叫你们等等吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.84,0:07:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊，对于一个不受伤害的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.28,0:07:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你打算怎么战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,笨蛋，你有什么办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也变成不死之身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不死之身？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种事做得到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以啊，只要吃下一碗仙豆就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.32,0:07:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪里有那么多的仙豆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.26,0:07:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是，这是把仙豆忘在厕所的人说的话吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我下次不会忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.62,0:07:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问题不在那里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.96,0:08:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有事情必须要告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.88,0:08:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.51,0:08:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未来的你还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.93,0:08:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.06,0:08:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.15,0:08:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没办法把她带到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没关系的，小舞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.47,0:08:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未来的小舞哪是这么容易被打败的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.29,0:08:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是，未来的你很强的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好像没见过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.27,0:08:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小舞一定还在等着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了帮助我逃回这里的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定要打倒他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.55,0:08:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过，对方是不死之身，要怎么做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.11,0:09:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,维斯先生，比鲁斯大人，连界王神大人也来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.08,0:09:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打扰各位了，悟空先生在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.93,0:09:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,界王神有很重要的事情要告诉你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.08,0:09:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.08,0:09:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨，有什么话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,界王神大人特意来到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.91,0:09:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总觉得有不好的预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实，有位叫祖诺的贤者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和我联系过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，祖诺啊？他还好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还…还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听祖诺说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.05,0:09:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有一位为了超级龙珠和孙悟空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.22,0:09:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特意从很远地方来找他的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了我吗，那是谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.17,0:10:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是扎马斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.92,0:10:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么要问超级龙珠的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.32,0:10:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也正好有事想和你们说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.43,0:10:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦，是什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.35,0:10:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，已经没有了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯，再来一壶茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.77,0:10:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.82,0:10:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去哪了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯是敌人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.95,0:10:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯是不死之身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超级赛亚人桃红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这名字听起来很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.29,0:10:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以需要你们的智慧，有什么办法消灭神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.88,0:10:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，这么轻松地提出这种可怕的要求啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道想和我打架吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为事情紧急啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.96,0:11:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯和「黑悟空」是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.07,0:11:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为何气会相似呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是偶然的相似而已吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.13,0:11:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此，原来是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.47,0:11:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祖诺的话，悟空先生他们未来的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,收集了很有意思的情报呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好像明白了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？什么？你明白了什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.72,0:11:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别卖关子了，告诉他们吧，维斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.89,0:11:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是，听了刚才这些事，我发觉了一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.89,0:11:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是，被称为天才的界王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被悟空先生打败过的扎马斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.52,0:11:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,执着于悟空先生，竟然去问祖诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.04,0:11:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这恐怕说明扎马斯正在寻求一种力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.29,0:12:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说，扎马斯需要坚持自己的正义的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们不这么认为吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.66,0:12:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以扎马斯需要得到拥有绝对力量的协助者的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.71,0:12:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是我发觉的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.80,0:12:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是超级龙珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.72,0:12:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不错，正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.06,0:12:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超级龙珠就是他必需的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.23,0:12:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真难得你战斗以外时脑子这么好使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.38,0:12:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说，扎马斯需要超级龙珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.22,0:12:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来完成他的这个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,制造出「黑悟空」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,制造出「黑悟空」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.52,0:13:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，猜错了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.73,0:13:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，我想悟空先生说对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎样，我很了不起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.20,0:13:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是，现在不是你得意的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有和你一样强的坏人存在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.20,0:13:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过这始终是现在的推测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是「黑悟空」他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.39,0:13:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用超级龙珠制造出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.84,0:13:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是孙悟空的复制品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.76,0:13:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我一个和孙悟空同样身体的仆人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.06,0:13:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就想得通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」是卡卡罗特的人偶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.19,0:13:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是他为什么要制造出一个悟空叔叔呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.10,0:13:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是他对前几日交过手的悟空先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.29,0:13:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,产生了兴趣导致的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.75,0:13:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的，都是你做的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.62,0:13:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.87,0:14:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后来扎马斯又等了一年时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.08,0:14:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到超级龙珠复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.34,0:14:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出来吧神之龙，实现我们的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,TYONMAGE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.64,0:14:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我不死的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.69,0:14:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.16,0:14:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不死之身，再加上毁灭人类的孙悟空的力量！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.41,0:14:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,执行正义的准备已经好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.39,0:14:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯和「黑悟空」攻击了未来的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一年是规矩的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一年，这可够让人心急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.85,0:15:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超级龙珠分布在两个宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本就不知道在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这扎马斯的忍耐力还真强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.19,0:15:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了，是时光戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.49,0:15:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用那个就不用等待一年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.45,0:15:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不错，可以马上去一年后的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.39,0:15:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，为什么「黑悟空」会有那种东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你去问他本人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.59,0:15:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」拜托扎马斯借来的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.80,0:15:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听着，时光戒指只有界王神可以使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是随便可以借着玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.18,0:15:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们知道的扎马斯现在不过是见习界王神而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们是从哪得到戒指的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.28,0:15:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第10宇宙的界王神大人和扎马斯之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.00,0:16:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定发生了很严重的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是这样吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常坏的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.33,0:16:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说，第10宇宙的界王神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.52,0:16:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,格瓦斯大人危在旦夕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.92,0:16:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么那个大叔会危险呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.05,0:16:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你刚才那股聪明劲都飞了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不明白？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.68,0:16:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯杀了格瓦斯，夺走了时光戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.69,0:16:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就可以随意从见习变为界王神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯变成了坏人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个家伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.95,0:16:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果这些是真的，未来是因为扎马斯的正义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.92,0:16:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,高歌正义的家伙没有好人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.13,0:16:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.26,0:17:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再去见一次扎马斯，确认一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.94,0:17:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们感觉到的「黑悟空」的气的真实身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在还是个谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.80,0:17:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」明明是悟空先生的复制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.95,0:17:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么只有气和扎马斯相同呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.95,0:17:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个谜什么时候能够解开呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.86,0:17:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过现在，还是担心格瓦斯大人的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.99,0:17:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来带大家过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.90,0:17:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过各位，拜托你们要息事宁人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在的扎马斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还没有具体做出什么行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要担心，特兰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.75,0:17:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我对现在的扎马斯没兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.38,0:17:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听你们讲，不过是个自大，讲大道理的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.06,0:17:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.73,0:17:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快坐上来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.94,0:17:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要，我才不要抓住女人的后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.57,0:18:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会被他们发现的，快点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.96,0:18:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小舞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真希，小治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯哥哥在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.26,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事，他在很远的地方努力着呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.26,0:18:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙悟空先生和贝吉塔先生都不是对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.06,0:18:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们没希望了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.27,0:18:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是战略性的撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敌人太强大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.57,0:18:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且还增加到两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本赢不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.20,0:18:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯先生他们真的会回来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然，绝对会的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.14,0:19:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很多人看着被轻松杀掉的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.43,0:19:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,认为只能放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以，不能放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.14,0:19:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有很多人为了地球的延续在努力着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家一定要团结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.14,0:19:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家要相信特兰克斯，等着他，活下去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.71,0:19:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好饿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.92,0:19:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.24,0:19:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀哎呀，怎么了吗，你们一起过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首先，看您没事我们就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.54,0:19:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.14,0:19:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们有急事想见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这…这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.94,0:19:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思，扎马斯他不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去哪了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.07,0:19:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.56,0:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.48,0:19:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯在未来不得了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.44,0:20:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛，比鲁斯大人您干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.44,0:20:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别说话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.88,0:20:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.88,0:20:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关于扎马斯有什么在意的地方吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.37,0:20:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您说的是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比如关于正义的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.54,0:20:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正义？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.12,0:20:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这件事的话，他已经茅塞顿开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.59,0:20:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,茅塞顿开？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.09,0:20:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯正在学习神的职责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.15,0:20:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不久就会成为界王神，守护这个第10宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.85,0:20:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他一边看着星球的兴衰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.44,0:20:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一边不断问着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.12,0:20:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类是什么，智慧是什么，神是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.11,0:20:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些问题的答案，让他茅塞顿开了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.87,0:20:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊，现在他的心很纯净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.31,0:20:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直以来，他因为神的存在，善与恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.00,0:21:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有自己的正义而迷失，苦恼过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.04,0:21:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过为了继任界王神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.12,0:21:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在他已经领悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.93,0:21:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.78,0:21:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,格瓦斯大人，请用茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咻咻咻　咻咻一瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.88,0:21:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,触碰在眉宇间的指尖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.43,0:21:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噔噔噔　头发已冲冠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.97,0:21:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,力量注满　这就是赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.56,0:21:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要迸发光芒的Shining Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.98,0:21:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,（小心喽！）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.27,0:21:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跳越时空隧道　未来的问候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.73,0:21:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的表情　如果我没有看错的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.28,0:21:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可不行　相信我　凭你的直觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.53,0:22:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若生命不息　追逐就不能停却
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.32,0:22:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直舞动　一直舞动　一直到永远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.91,0:22:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,(Ooh- HEY!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.08,0:22:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yoka Yoka Dance! (HEY!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.33,0:22:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yoka Yoka Dance! (HEY!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.54,0:22:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yoka Yoka Yoka Yoka Yoka Yoka Yoka Yoka Dance! (龟派气功!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.21,0:22:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yoka Yoka Dance! (HEY!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.33,0:22:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yoka Yoka Dance! (HEY!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.71,0:22:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yoka Yoka Yoka Yoka Yoka Yoka Yoka Yoka
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.17,0:22:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只～要你舞动　你就能找到笑容（Hoo Hoo）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.22,0:22:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只因为你舞动　你自然有了笑容（Yoka Yoka）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.76,0:22:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使一路坎坷　艰难重重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.52,0:22:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也要笑傲天地之间　苦中作乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.19,0:22:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就让我们齐心合力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.90,0:22:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竭尽全力　共舞长空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.18,0:22:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨，我是悟空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.16,0:22:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯真的要杀格瓦斯大人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.44,0:22:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那当然不能袖手旁观了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.16,0:22:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必须马上阻止扎马斯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.95,0:22:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要证据吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.87,0:22:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被杀了就太迟了，比鲁斯大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.07,0:22:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他到底要做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.91,0:22:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下集『龙珠超』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.99,0:23:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「保护界王神格瓦斯 破坏扎马斯！」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要看啊

